resources.string: " It is a really simple playing for fun slot machine. It uses random numbers and prizes are not in real money. \n The usage is very simple. Load credit and push the spin button. \n Have fun!"

" Tuty Fruty Slot for Android is published by Velbazhd Software LLC. 
 This is a playing for fun slot machine game (no gambling). It has five reels, three rows and set of betting lines. 
 Newer versions can be checked at: 
 http://github.com/TodorBalabanov/tuty-fruty-slot-for-android"
